-- ACCENTS IN ITALIAN:
we have two accents:
--> ACCENTO ACUTO: (√®) -> will stress the sound of the word in an acute way: T√® (tea)
--> ACCNTO GRAVE (√©) -> will stress with a lower sound. only exists with E (perch√©, poich√©)

